description:
This is a 23 minute workout called 'HIIT Workout - Insane 20 Minute Elliptical Workout' from the channel AbundantYou with Dr Kevin.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Dr. Kevin Sarich DC, demonstrates another insane 20 minute HIIT workout using an elliptical to reach your fitness goals in minimal time. This is a workout you definitely want to try!

The elliptical is a mainstay in the gym for good reason: it's easy on the joints and provides a great cardio and total-body workout. But the elliptical can also get pretty boring and repetitive. 

This elliptical workout will for sure change things up in a good way you're looking for!

HIIT workouts - known as High Intensity Interval Training, are the most effective way to burn fat in the shortest amount of time possible. However, most people don't utilize this type of workout enough. 

It's recommend to perform a 10-30 minute HIIT workout 2-3 times a week, with 24 hour rest in between HIIT workouts, in addition to other variety of fitness activities.
